of one last perfect Christmas.

19:00.560 --> 19:02.608
And I know that you think
that I'm ridiculous...

19:02.680 --> 19:04.409
No, I don't think
you're being ridiculous.

19:04.480 --> 19:06.721
Under the circumstances, yeah,
you are being a little ridiculous.

19:06.800 --> 19:09.644
<i>♪ ...Comfort and joy
Comfort and joy</i>

19:09.720 --> 19:14.248
