I'm going to tell them the truth.

19:30.960 --> 19:32.200
We'll all be together.
Wait a minute.

19:32.280 --> 19:33.611
No, we made an agreement.

19:33.680 --> 19:35.489
You cannot break an agreement,
mid-agreement.

19:35.560 --> 19:37.449
