a brown young virgin?

28:01.200 --> 28:02.361
And her mother
and her child.

28:02.440 --> 28:03.601
Oh, my God.

28:03.680 --> 28:05.409
I didn't write the song,
Charlotte.

28:05.480 --> 28:07.084
Look, Sam,
I was a music teacher.

28:07.160 --> 28:10.004
Round. That's what it is.
She's a round young virgin.

28:10.080 --> 28:11.969
