29:32.680 --> 29:34.284
All right.

29:34.360 --> 29:35.800
Did you always want to
join the army?

29:36.760 --> 29:39.161
Uh, it's a long story.

29:39.240 --> 29:40.844
Oh.

29:40.920 --> 29:42.206
Father in the military?

29:42.280 --> 29:43.805
Mm-hmm.

29:43.880 --> 29:45.769
Short story, really.

