29:54.040 --> 29:55.485
What if I was wrong?

29:55.560 --> 29:58.131
That certainty,
that's amazing.

29:58.200 --> 30:00.248
Thank you.
In like a...

30:00.360 --> 30:03.523
corporate-loving, government-trusting,
gung-ho kind of way.

30:03.600 --> 30:04.726
Uh-huh.

30:04.800 --> 30:07.770
