01:12:00.240 --> 01:12:01.605
Yes?

01:12:01.680 --> 01:12:03.011
Merry Christmas.

01:12:10.440 --> 01:12:11.965
Thanks for the ride.

01:12:13.040 --> 01:12:14.041
If I ask you a question,

01:12:15.160 --> 01:12:16.286
